ation digs into various data storage techniques and using the cloud in a way that doesn't break the bank. Jeff may be a Microsoft employee, but that doesn't mean he uses only Microsoft tools for his projects. Duration: 57 minutes.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-06-07T19:55:37.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"beardicus/awesome-plotters","categoryHTML":"<h2>Hardware</h2><h3>Pens</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.printables.com/model/156721-sharpie-fine-point-plotter-adapter\">Sharpie Fine Point Plotter Adapter</a> - 3d-printed adapter to fit a standard Sharpie in an HP-GL plotter.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-06-07T19:49:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"beardicus/awesome-plotters","categoryHTML":"<h2>Hardware</h2><h3>Pens</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.printables.com/model/156722-plotter-pen\">Plotter Pen STL Models</a> - Accurate STL models of both short and long standard plotter pens.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-06-07T19:49:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"beardicus/awesome-plotters","categoryHTML":"<h2>Inspiration, Instruction, and Research</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/quarterstudio/an-intro-to-pen-plotters-29b6bd4327ba\">An Intro to Pen Plotters</a> - Good info on getting started with old HPGL plotters .</li>","updatedAt":"2022-06-07T19:49:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"beardicus/awesome-plotters","categoryHTML":"<h2>Hardware</h2><h3>Plotters</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://shop.evilmadscientist.com/productsmenu/846\">AxiDraw</a> - Pen plotter from <a href=\"https://www.evilmadscientist.com\">Evil Mad Scientist</a>, very popular on #plottertwitter.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-06-07T18:48:10.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"beardicus/awesome-plotters","categoryHTML":"<h2>Hardware</h2><h3>Plotters</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:2349232\">Drawing Robot</a> - 3d-Printable AxiDraw clone w/ Arduino CNC Shield controller running grbl firmware.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-06-07T18:48:10.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"beardicus/awes